      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry i didnt mean to make it sound weird lol. i just want to know the math part. if i have a $300k loan, and the rate jumps from 4% to 7% after the 5 years are up, what does that do to my monthly payment roughly? i need to know if i can actually afford the jump.",
